      <title>挪威建议不要与以色列定居点进行贸易和商业往来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/norway-advises-against-trade-business-with-israeli-settlements</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威政府不鼓励该国公司开展有助于维护以色列定居点的贸易和商业活动，这突显了其现有立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/norway-advises-against-trade-business-with-israeli-settlements</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
