    <item>
      <title>欧盟提议因阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼之死对俄罗斯实施新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/eu-proposes-new-russia-sanctions-over-death-of-alexey-navalny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将就俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼上个月在北极监狱死亡事件提出新的制裁措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/eu-proposes-new-russia-sanctions-over-death-of-alexey-navalny</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:18:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非非国大将在投票后实施指定资产计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/south-africa-s-anc-to-pursue-prescribed-assets-plan-after-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政的非洲人国民大会将继续推进恢复种族隔离时代规则的计划，迫使养老基金将资金投入某些政府批准的投资，前提是它在即将到来的选举中保留权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/south-africa-s-anc-to-pursue-prescribed-assets-plan-after-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:01:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛称俄罗斯为波罗的海长期对峙做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/russia-prepares-for-long-term-standoff-in-baltic-lithuania-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛间谍机构称，随着克里姆林宫向西扩大军事能力，俄罗斯军方正在准备与北约成员国在波罗的海地区发生长期对峙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/russia-prepares-for-long-term-standoff-in-baltic-lithuania-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧尔班与央行行长的不和引发投资者警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/orban-s-feud-with-central-bank-chief-in-hungary-triggers-investor-alarm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理维克托·欧尔班花了几个月的时间敦促匈牙利央行更积极地降息，使该国摆脱衰退。紧张局势正在演变为公开冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/orban-s-feud-with-central-bank-chief-in-hungary-triggers-investor-alarm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国在罢工期间为紧急护理人员增加资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/south-korea-adds-funds-for-emergency-care-staff-during-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国将增加对在医生罢工导致人员短缺期间维持急诊室运转的医院的补偿，并正在推进一项提高医学院入学率的计划，该计划引发了劳工行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/south-korea-adds-funds-for-emergency-care-staff-during-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:18:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国警告美国贸易限制的“荒谬”将损害美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-slams-us-for-monopolizing-tech-as-biden-seen-pushing-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部长谴责美国对这个亚洲国家实施“令人困惑”的贸易限制，因为美国总统乔·拜登阻​​止北京接触先进技术的努力破坏了世界最大两个经济体之间稳定的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-slams-us-for-monopolizing-tech-as-biden-seen-pushing-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:38:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国专家组推进禁令法案后，药明康德和药明生物股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/wuxi-apptec-drops-as-us-senate-panel-advances-bill-banning-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院委员会提出一项法案，该法案可能禁止中国生物技术公司获得联邦合同，并在很大程度上切断这家生物制药公司占其收入一半以上的市场的份额，导致药明康德股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/wuxi-apptec-drops-as-us-senate-panel-advances-bill-banning-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔总统萨勒下台前急于解决选举混乱问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/senegal-sets-march-presidential-vote-before-end-of-sall-s-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔定于本月举行选举，尽管该国最高法院和政府设定了不同的投票日期，因为该国急于在现任总统麦基·萨尔任期结束前选举新总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/senegal-sets-march-presidential-vote-before-end-of-sall-s-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装沉船的锚可能切断海上互联网电缆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/anchor-from-houthi-sunk-ship-likely-damaged-undersea-cables</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国和一个行业组织的评估，2月底，胡塞武装分子击沉的一艘货船的锚可能损坏了红海的三根电信电缆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/anchor-from-houthi-sunk-ship-likely-damaged-undersea-cables</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 17:03:33 GMT</pubDate>
